collection.name: Boss Beauties
collection.description:
A Woman can be Everything she wants.

For 10 years, it has been our mission to educate and empower the next generation of Women and Girls. The Boss Beauties Collection is an extension of the same passion and goals we have championed for the past decade. 

All Boss Beauties holders receive utilities such as tickets to our exclusive music festival, NFT drops, licensing rights and exclusive access to our future partner collaborations (Boss Beauties partners have included Marvel, Barbie, Hugo Boss, Neiman Marcus, Rolling Stone and more)
